text: Nils Lagerlöf (born August 14, 1995) is a Swedish former professional ice hockey defenceman. He last played for the Kallinge-Ronneby IF of the Hockeyettan. Lagerlöf made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Frölunda HC during the 2014–15 SHL season.http://www.frolundaindians.com/andralag/J20/867 ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Frölunda HC players Category:Swedish ice hockey defencemen
